## Bug 2 — Controller Input Lag

**Platform:** PlayStation 5
**Severity:** High
**Frequency:** Consistent during online matches

**Steps to Reproduce:**
1. Launch EA FC 26
2. Start any online match
3. Use standard controller settings
4. Press pass button (X) during active gameplay

**Expected:** Ball passes instantly on button press
**Actual:** 1-2 second delay before pass executes
**Impact:** Directly affects competitive timing and fairness

## Bug 3 — Finesse Shot PlayStyle Weak Output
**Platform:** PlayStation 5
**Severity:** High
